OL,3,CMan convicted of killing heavily
OL,4,Cpregnant teen's unborn baby
OL,6,FA man has been convicted of killing
OL,7,Fhis heavily pregnant 17-year-old
OL,8,Fpartner's unborn baby during a
OL,9,F"disturbing, violent and harrowing"
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FStefan Marin, 19, assaulted the girl
OL,13,Fat his flat before telling her to
OL,14,Fchange into clean clothes and forcing
OL,15,Fher to leave with him and abandoning
OL,16,Fher in the street.
OL,18,FShe was found collapsed by a member of
OL,19,Fthe public, bleeding and barely
OL,20,Fconscious.
