OL,4,Cpregnant teen's unborn baby
OL,6,FScans revealed the loss of her baby at
OL,7,F29 weeks gestation.
OL,9,FMarin, of George Street Hull, was
OL,10,Ffound guilty of child destruction
OL,11,Ffollowing the first successful
OL,12,Fprosecution of its kind by Humberside
OL,13,FPolice and only the fourth in the
OL,14,Fcountry in the last 10 years.
OL,16,FHe was also convicted of grievous
OL,17,Fbodily harm with intent, non-fatal
OL,18,Fstrangulation, false imprisonment and
OL,19,Fperverting the course of justice.
