OL,6,FMarin will be sentenced at a later
OL,7,Fdate.
OL,9,FWhat is the offence of child
OL,10,Fdestruction?
OL,12,FUnder the 1929 Infant Life
OL,13,F(Preservation) Act, the life of a
OL,14,Fviable unborn child is protected.
OL,15,FGestation of 28 weeks or more is
OL,16,Fconsidered proof of a viable pregnancy.
OL,18,FChild destruction is the specific
OL,19,Fcrime of intentionally causing a child
OL,20,Fto die before it is born alive.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
