OL,6,FThe law does not apply if the act was
OL,7,Fa legal abortion or was done in good
OL,8,Ffaith to save the life of the mother.
OL,9,FChild destruction is punishable by
OL,10,Flife imprisonment.
OL,12,FHull Crown Court heard Marin punched,
OL,13,Fkicked, strangled and scalded the girl
OL,14,Fduring a four-hour attack at his home
OL,15,Fon 13 March 2025.
OL,17,FShe was found in the street at around
OL,18,F10.20pm and was taken to hospital
OL,19,Fwhere it was found she had suffered a
OL,20,Fbroken nose and major trauma to her
OL,21,Fbody as well as the loss of her baby.
