OL,6,FCCTV footage captured Marin walking
OL,7,Fthe teenager to the top of an alleyway
OL,8,Fand leaving her there. He warned that
OL,9,Fhe would harm her family if she told
OL,10,Fanyone.
OL,12,FWhen police went to Marin's home, they
OL,13,Ffound it had been cleaned and smelt
OL,14,Fstrongly of bleach. Her discarded
OL,15,Fclothing was found outside the
OL,16,Fproperty.
OL,18,FMarin was found guilty after a nine-
OL,19,Fday trial.
