OL,6,FIn a statement the victim said: "What
OL,7,Fhappened to me was something no one
OL,8,Fshould ever have to go through. I was
OL,9,Fbeaten for hours and suffered injuries
OL,10,Fthat permanently changed my life - but
OL,11,Fthe greatest pain of all was losing my
OL,12,Fbaby boy.
OL,14,F"I've had to find strength I never
OL,15,Fknew I had and, while nothing can
OL,16,Fbring my baby back, I hope that by
OL,17,Fspeaking out, I can help others who
OL,18,Fare living with abuse realise there is
OL,19,Fa way out and that they are not alone."
