OL,6,FShe added: "I will live in comfort
OL,7,Fhoping his legacy can help others, by
OL,8,Finspiring positive changes in the law
OL,9,Ffor victims and that justice has
OL,10,Ffinally been served for both of us."
OL,12,FDet Ch Insp Jon Cross, of Humberside
OL,13,FPolice, said: "This was a deeply
OL,14,Fdisturbing, violent, and harrowing
OL,15,Fattack on a vulnerable young girl,
OL,16,Fwhich resulted in the unfathomable
OL,17,Floss of her child that was just weeks
OL,18,Faway from being born.
