OL,6,F"Marin's actions were calculated and
OL,7,Futterly inhumane. After subjecting her
OL,8,Fto hours of sustained violence, he
OL,9,Fthen left her alone in the street,
OL,10,Fknowing full well the extent of her
OL,11,Finjuries. That level of disregard for
OL,12,Fher life and wellbeing is truly
OL,13,Fappalling."
OL,15,FEdmund Hall, senior crown prosecutor
OL,16,Ffrom the Crown Prosecution Service,
OL,17,Fsaid: "This was a brutal crime, where
OL,18,Fthe defendant viciously assaulted not
OL,19,Fonly a young girl, but also a
OL,20,Fdefenceless unborn baby.
