OL,6,F"The CPS carefully considered the
OL,7,Fevidence and a further charge of child
OL,8,Fdestruction, a rarely committed
OL,9,Foffence, which was authorised and
OL,10,Fadded to the indictment.
OL,12,F"The CPS thanks Humberside Police for
OL,13,Fa thorough investigation, and above
OL,14,Fall the girl herself, who has
OL,15,Fdisplayed courage far beyond her years
OL,16,Fin giving evidence to obtain justice
OL,17,Ffor her unborn baby."
